listy = [{'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020905-2.gif', 'alt_text': "This was literally the first single panel comic idea I ever had, though it isn't the first drawing. I revised it around 2005 or so, at a point when I apparently thought fingertips were square-shaped.", 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-07'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020907-2.gif', 'alt_text': "Actually there's a little post-it chastising you for your own insecurities.", 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-09'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020909-2.gif', 'alt_text': 'The real error here was using a level 1 spell on a level 5 opponent.', 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-16'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020916-2.gif', 'alt_text': 'Really? All that and you still want hovertext? Go read a book.', 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-17'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020917-2.gif', 'alt_text': 'Tom was so disconnected from his own feelings that he offered gold and jewels whenever expressing himself. By the time he and Sally had been together for five years, he had begun to understand that his emotional weaknesses should be shared with the woman he loved most. But, it was too late. With the millions of dollars in rings, she had escaped to Argentina, and love.', 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-20'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020920-2.gif', 'alt_text': "Fifteen years after writing this cartoon, I realize this isn't how Russian Roulette works.", 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-21'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020921-2.gif', 'alt_text': 'The part where Ophelia turns out to have survived by secretly being a mermaid was pretty good, though.', 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-22'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020922-2.gif', 'alt_text': "It later turns out they're just in Texas.", 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-09-27'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/20020927-2.gif', 'alt_text': "There should've been a moment where Vader just quiets down and gets sarcastic with Luke. 'Oh, you lost an arm. Wow, I bet that's super painful. Can't imagine what that's like.'", 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-10-03'}, {'image_url': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comics/1425480626-20021003-2.gif', 'alt_text': 'Fun Fact: When I switched to doing single panels in 2002, after having done short character-based strips for a bit, an early reader identified this particular comic as the reason she stopped reading. This was a bit distressing, since at the time, that one reader was about 10 percent of my audience.', 'next_link': 'https://www.smbc-comics.com/comic/2002-10-07'}]